            <p>
               <gap unit="character" extent="unknown" reason="lost"/> the copy <supplied reason="lost">of the inscription was deposited in the property-archive in the staphanephorate</supplied> of Tib<ex>erius</ex> Cl<ex>audius</ex> Diogenes, ?month <supplied reason="lost">of</supplied>
               <gap unit="character" extent="unknown" reason="lost"/>
