         <div type="commentary">
            <p>ll. 1, 2 seem beyond interpretation.</p>
            <p> ll. 3, 4 can be restored with high probability as from a penal formula (so already Cormack). We offer a standard wording, but there is some variety in texts without real differences in meaning.</p>
